staxel.village.character.dialogue.JamieL: (안함)I have so many ideas but I can only make one a reality...
(안함)It has to be the very best!
(안함)Honestly, I don't know what I did to offend those execs.
(안함)I only mailed them a few hundred times.
(안함)It's not like I stood outside their windows and waved at them!
(안함)At least...not more than once or twice...
